BUGS
====

- rmdir: Handle pagination for clear_container


FEATURES
========

- Named-endpoints

# Use default endpoint
bashfiles get container foo

# Use 'bar' endpoint
bashfiles -e bar get container foo

Option 1

~/.bashfiles
[default]
BF_SERVICE=CF
CF_USERNAME=myuser

Option 2

~/.bashfiles-config/
    default.endpoint
        BF_SERVICE=CF
        CF_USERNAME=myuser


Option 3

~/.bashfiles-config/
    endpoints/
        default/
            config
                BF_SERVICE=CF
                CF_USERNAME=myuser

            completion/
                container-names
                <container>-object-names


CRUD:

bashfiles endpoints ls
bashfiles endpoints add bar
bashfiles endpoints rm bar





